// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1554 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 92f2b85b-afc8-5a54-9c4d-50347c9284c3

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
